104
00:05:37.754 --> 00:05:39.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>That'll be all, Lieutenant.</c.bg_transparent>

105
00:05:39.547 --> 00:05:41.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Sir?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Dismissed.</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:05:51.225 --> 00:05:53.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You asked for me, Commander?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I've been thinking.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:05:54.479 --> 00:05:57.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no guarantee</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the Imperial Guard's gonna believe us.</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:05:57.732 --> 00:06:00.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got no evidence</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your people are planning this attack.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:06:00.610 --> 00:06:03.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>But there is one Andorian</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who might trust us.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:06:03.946 --> 00:06:06.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>At least he does some of the time.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:06:06.115 --> 00:06:07.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Commander Shran.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:06:07.575 --> 00:06:09.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Problem is,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I have no idea how to find him.</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:06:10.995 --> 00:06:13.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I may be able to help.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:06:14.457 --> 00:06:15.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:06:17.960 --> 00:06:20.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant Reed appeared unsettled.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:06:21.881 --> 00:06:25.051 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Some of the crew are wondering</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if I'm doing the right thing.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:06:26.135 --> 00:06:29.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can't say I blame them.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not so sure myself.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:06:29.847 --> 00:06:34.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have no doubt Captain Archer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would pursue this same course of action.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:06:36.020 --> 00:06:37.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's what I keep telling myself.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:06:45.571 --> 00:06:48.783 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>will be scanning for us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the transport coordinates.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:06:48.866 --> 00:06:50.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One of us should go there.</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:06:50.326 --> 00:06:52.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's too dangerous.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We're staying together.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:06:52.495 --> 00:06:55.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Taking the artifact to the High Command</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will accomplish nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:06:55.623 --> 00:06:57.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It might be the only thing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that can stop the war.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:06:57.708 --> 00:06:58.835 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What war?</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:06:58.918 --> 00:07:00.711 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Between Vulcan and Andoria.</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:07:00.795 --> 00:07:04.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We settled our dispute</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the Andorians nearly two years ago.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:07:04.382 --> 00:07:06.592 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>V'Las was just stalling for time.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:07:06.676 --> 00:07:09.470 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's been preparing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a large-scale attack ever since.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:07:09.554 --> 00:07:11.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where did you get this information?</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:07:12.765 --> 00:07:13.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where do you think?</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:07:16.769 --> 00:07:21.232 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Assuming for the moment</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you possess Surak's Katra,</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:07:21.315 --> 00:07:23.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>he's been dead for centuries.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:07:23.276 --> 00:07:25.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How could he be aware of plans for a war?</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:07:25.945 --> 00:07:29.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Some of Syrran's memories</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>must have been transferred in the meld.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:07:31.701 --> 00:07:33.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:07:34.078 --> 00:07:35.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You think I've lost my mind?</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:07:35.455 --> 00:07:38.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not certain your mind</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is the one making these decisions.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:07:41.836 --> 00:07:43.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We should return to the ship.</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:07:43.754 --> 00:07:45.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pau can take the artifact</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the capital.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:07:45.840 --> 00:07:48.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was chosen for this.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:07:48.259 --> 00:07:49.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chosen?</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:07:49.594 --> 00:07:52.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Interesting choice of words.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:07:52.388 --> 00:07:54.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I were in your shoes,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'd be just as skeptical.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:07:54.682 --> 00:07:56.392 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:07:56.476 --> 00:08:00.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not possessed and I'm not delusional.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:08:00.271 --> 00:08:02.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are forces at work</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on your world right now,</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:08:02.899 --> 00:08:06.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>trying to undo everything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Surak taught your people.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:08:06.235 --> 00:08:09.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we fail,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Vulcan will be consumed by them.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:08:09.906 --> 00:08:12.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's why we have to get</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>this thing to the capital.</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:08:12.533 --> 00:08:14.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And I'm gonna need</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>all three of us to try and find--</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:08:14.994 --> 00:08:17.079 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Archer! Don't move.</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:08:18.873 --> 00:08:20.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Gallicite deposits.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:08:20.458 --> 00:08:23.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you in possession</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of anything metallic?</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:08:25.588 --> 00:08:26.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just this.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:08:30.051 --> 00:08:32.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( electricity buzzing )</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:08:35.181 --> 00:08:37.016 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks for the warning.</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:08:42.813 --> 00:08:44.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our patrol has returned.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:08:44.732 --> 00:08:46.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They captured eight Syrrannites</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the sanctuary.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:08:46.859 --> 00:08:48.569 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Was Syrran among them?</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:08:48.653 --> 00:08:50.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. He is dead.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:08:50.988 --> 00:08:55.910 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Syrrannites say that there were</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>three other survivors, including a human.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:08:56.827 --> 00:08:57.912 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Archer.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:08:57.995 --> 00:09:00.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They say that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he is carrying the Kir'Shara.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:09:01.040 --> 00:09:03.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Kir'Shara never existed.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:09:03.668 --> 00:09:08.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are scholars who believe it does</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and that it was hidden in the forge.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:09:08.714 --> 00:09:09.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Syrrannites claim</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:09:10.049 --> 00:09:12.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that they are following</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the true path of Surak.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:09:13.010 --> 00:09:16.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If the Kir'Shara is real,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it could prove them right.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:09:16.347 --> 00:09:18.349 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't exist!</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:09:19.892 --> 00:09:22.645 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've been listening</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to Syrrannite propaganda.</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:09:23.563 --> 00:09:25.773 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That will be all, Minister.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:09:41.372 --> 00:09:44.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sublieutenant, order Major Talok</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:09:44.917 --> 00:09:47.378 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to find the remaining Syrrannites.</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:09:47.461 --> 00:09:50.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're dealing with radical insurgents.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:09:52.842 --> 00:09:54.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're to be eradicated.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:09:55.636 --> 00:09:57.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do I make myself clear?</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:10:06.480 --> 00:10:08.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Open a channel.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:10:09.066 --> 00:10:11.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-To who?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-The Nebula.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:10:15.865 --> 00:10:17.908 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( beep )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-This is Ambassador Soval.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:10:17.992 --> 00:10:19.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've come on an urgent mission.</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:10:19.952 --> 00:10:22.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I must speak with Commander Shran.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:10:25.416 --> 00:10:28.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The High Command has decrypted</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your security protocols.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:10:28.919 --> 00:10:33.007 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're well aware that your task force</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has been hiding in this nebula.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:10:34.967 --> 00:10:37.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe your information's out of date.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:10:37.928 --> 00:10:39.305 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's in there.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:10:42.224 --> 00:10:44.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is Commander Tucker of </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise.</i></c.bg_transparent>

188
00:10:44.977 --> 00:10:49.023 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got some information</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you're gonna want to hear.</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:10:49.106 --> 00:10:51.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( computer beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:10:51.567 --> 00:10:52.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:10:58.824 --> 00:11:00.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( beep )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-We're being hailed.</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:11:02.495 --> 00:11:07.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Commander Tucker,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>you have a poor choice of friends.</i></c.bg_transparent>

193
00:11:10.169 --> 00:11:11.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>An invasion?</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:11:12.004 --> 00:11:13.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's correct.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:11:13.381 --> 00:11:15.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We keep a very close eye on your fleet.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:11:15.549 --> 00:11:17.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We would know if the High Command</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were preparing to attack.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:11:18.010 --> 00:11:20.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>V'Las has been assembling ships</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>near Regulus,</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:11:20.638 --> 00:11:22.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>beyond the range</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of your listening stations.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:11:22.973 --> 00:11:26.060 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your leaders may be fools,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but they're not suicidal.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:11:26.143 --> 00:11:28.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They know we will respond.</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:11:28.437 --> 00:11:30.606 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They were told</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you're adapting Xindi weaponry</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:11:30.689 --> 00:11:32.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and that you're planning</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to use it against Vulcan.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:11:32.942 --> 00:11:34.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's absurd!</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:11:34.235 --> 00:11:35.778 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain Archer</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>destroyed the Xindi prototype</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:11:35.861 --> 00:11:37.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>before we could examine it.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:11:37.446 --> 00:11:40.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That fact was conveniently omitted.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:11:40.533 --> 00:11:43.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You people are so used to lying,</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:11:43.327 --> 00:11:45.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you don't even tell</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the truth to each other!</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:11:45.746 --> 00:11:48.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do I know you weren't</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sent here as a diversion?</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:11:48.374 --> 00:11:49.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:11:50.000 --> 00:11:56.090 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you have any idea what will happen</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when the Imperial Guard retaliates?</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:11:56.799 --> 00:11:59.510 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It will be a disaster for both our worlds!</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:11:59.593 --> 00:12:03.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Which is why you must convince them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to intercept our fleet.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:12:05.182 --> 00:12:08.769 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're betraying your own people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by telling me this.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:12:08.853 --> 00:12:11.605 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm aware of that.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Why are you doing it?</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:12:12.606 --> 00:12:15.651 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The High Command is counting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on the element of surprise.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:12:15.734 --> 00:12:17.027 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If they meet resistance,</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:12:17.111 --> 00:12:20.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I believe V'Las will be forced</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to call off the invasion.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:12:24.410 --> 00:12:28.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>When does this invasion begin?</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:12:28.747 --> 00:12:30.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Soon.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:12:30.124 --> 00:12:32.877 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's the best you can give me... Soon?</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:12:33.419 --> 00:12:34.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:12:36.380 --> 00:12:38.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you believe him, pink-skin?</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:12:38.466 --> 00:12:40.009 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wouldn't be here if I didn't.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:12:49.768 --> 00:12:52.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll need to consult with my superiors.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:12:52.521 --> 00:12:54.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suggest you do it fast.</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:13:09.246 --> 00:13:11.165 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'POL: That's the fourth patrol today.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:13:11.248 --> 00:13:13.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's an extensive security grid</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>around the capital.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:13:13.959 --> 00:13:16.086 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's unlikely we'll get past it.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:13:16.170 --> 00:13:18.047 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll find a way.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:13:18.130 --> 00:13:19.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Surak will help us.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:13:23.177 --> 00:13:25.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't believe in the Katra?</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:13:26.347 --> 00:13:28.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's irrelevant what I believe.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:13:28.974 --> 00:13:32.811 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Captain could be permanently injured</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if we don't get him to a doctor soon.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:13:32.895 --> 00:13:35.147 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He doesn't need a physician.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He needs a priest...</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:13:35.231 --> 00:13:37.733 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One experienced with Katras.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:13:41.862 --> 00:13:45.407 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's irrational that we're following</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>someone in his state of mind.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:13:46.825 --> 00:13:49.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What if he dies before we can get help?</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:13:53.123 --> 00:13:54.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I apologize.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:13:55.668 --> 00:13:59.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My mother's death has affected me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>more than I realized.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:13:59.338 --> 00:14:02.049 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was a great loss.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:14:02.132 --> 00:14:05.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We disagreed frequently,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but I valued her counsel.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:14:07.471 --> 00:14:11.183 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could allow you to experience</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what she shared with me.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:14:13.727 --> 00:14:15.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You melded with her?</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:14:19.358 --> 00:14:21.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I cannot meld.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:14:21.110 --> 00:14:22.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would initiate it.</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:14:23.988 --> 00:14:25.573 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not what I mean.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:14:27.533 --> 00:14:30.035 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was forced...</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:14:30.119 --> 00:14:33.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>To participate in a meld</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>several years ago.</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:14:33.372 --> 00:14:36.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was infected with a neural disease.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:14:36.584 --> 00:14:38.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pa'Nar Syndrome.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:14:39.712 --> 00:14:41.088 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you still suffer from it?</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:14:41.922 --> 00:14:43.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no cure.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:14:43.799 --> 00:14:47.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Another lie perpetrated</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by the High Command.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:14:47.511 --> 00:14:50.472 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pa'Nar has been known since Surak's time.</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:14:50.556 --> 00:14:54.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's caused by melders who have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>been improperly trained.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:14:54.602 --> 00:14:58.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>One with great experience</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can correct the neurological imbalance.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:14:58.564 --> 00:15:00.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is this something you can do?</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:15:10.451 --> 00:15:13.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My mind to your mind.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:15:13.203 --> 00:15:15.623 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My thoughts to your thoughts.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:15:17.041 --> 00:15:19.376 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our minds are merging.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:15:23.005 --> 00:15:24.715 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our minds are one.</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:15:30.638 --> 00:15:33.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-FEMALE: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Bridge to Commander Shran.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-This is Shran.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:15:33.849 --> 00:15:37.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We've isolated the Vulcan's</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>bio-signature.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>He's alone.</i></c.bg_transparent>

265
00:15:37.770 --> 00:15:40.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're certain </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>won't detect the transport?</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:15:40.397 --> 00:15:42.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>All they'll see is a brief energy surge.</i></c.bg_transparent>

267
00:15:42.399 --> 00:15:45.235 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>They'll think it came from the nebula.</i></c.bg_transparent>

268
00:15:45.319 --> 00:15:46.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Commander?</i></c.bg_transparent>

269
00:15:48.614 --> 00:15:50.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Energize when ready.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:15:50.324 --> 00:15:51.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALE: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Yes, sir.</i></c.bg_transparent>

271
00:15:53.243 --> 00:15:54.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:15:57.289 --> 00:15:59.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Welcome aboard, Ambassador.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:16:05.422 --> 00:16:08.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you're expecting me to plead for mercy,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'll be waiting a long time.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:16:09.009 --> 00:16:12.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I simply want to know</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your fleet's actual location.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:16:12.096 --> 00:16:13.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've already given it to you.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:16:13.973 --> 00:16:17.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then consider this our way of</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>confirming what you've told us.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:16:17.893 --> 00:16:19.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You didn't expect the Imperial Guard</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:16:19.853 --> 00:16:22.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to mobilize its entire fleet</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>based on nothing more</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:16:22.481 --> 00:16:25.776 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>than the word</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of one loyal Vulcan diplomat?</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:16:25.859 --> 00:16:30.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We spent weeks arguing over details</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in our treaty negotiations.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:16:30.447 --> 00:16:34.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Did I ever mislead you?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:16:35.494 --> 00:16:40.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You must know that torture</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is rarely effective against Vulcans.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:16:40.207 --> 00:16:43.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our mental disciplines</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>allow us to suppress pain.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:16:43.252 --> 00:16:46.046 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our security division has had</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a great deal of experience</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:16:46.130 --> 00:16:49.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>extracting information</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from Vulcan operatives.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:16:49.633 --> 00:16:53.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This machine doesn't</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>cause physical discomfort.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:16:53.095 --> 00:16:58.267 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It uses a neuro-synaptic field</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to lower your emotional threshold.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:17:04.648 --> 00:17:05.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:17:06.025 --> 00:17:07.609 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you feel?</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:17:07.693 --> 00:17:09.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping )</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:17:13.407 --> 00:17:17.870 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've seen Vulcans who were</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>broken by this device.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:17:17.953 --> 00:17:19.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They were never the same again.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:17:19.872 --> 00:17:23.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have no desire</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to see that happen to you.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:17:23.250 --> 00:17:26.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Where is your fleet?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I told you.</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:17:26.295 --> 00:17:28.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our ships are assembling near Regulus.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:17:30.883 --> 00:17:32.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( electronic whining )</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:17:32.926 --> 00:17:34.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( whimpers ) Release me!</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:17:34.803 --> 00:17:38.182 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't... Not until I'm certain</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you've told us the truth.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:17:38.265 --> 00:17:42.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then I suggest you increase the setting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and get this over with!</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:17:46.065 --> 00:17:47.066 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( electronic whining )</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:17:47.357 --> 00:17:49.318 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( screaming )</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:17:50.527 --> 00:17:51.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is it?</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:17:51.945 --> 00:17:53.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Ambassador seems to be missing.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:17:53.864 --> 00:17:57.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's not in his quarters</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or anywhere on "D" deck.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:17:57.618 --> 00:18:00.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( computer beeps )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Tucker to Soval.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:18:01.413 --> 00:18:03.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ambassador, please respond.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:18:05.334 --> 00:18:07.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Internal sensors...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Scan for his bio-signs.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:18:09.546 --> 00:18:10.881 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's not onboard.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:18:15.094 --> 00:18:16.720 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Scan the Andorian ships.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:18:18.555 --> 00:18:22.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's a Vulcan signature</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on their lead ship.</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:18:22.267 --> 00:18:24.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go to tactical alert. Open a channel.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:18:25.938 --> 00:18:27.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is Commander Tucker.</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:18:27.731 --> 00:18:30.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We know Ambassador Soval's</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>aboard your ship.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:18:30.567 --> 00:18:33.070 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to speak with him now.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:18:36.365 --> 00:18:38.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir, the Andorians</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>are moving toward the nebula.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:18:38.992 --> 00:18:41.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Target Shran's ship. Disable the engines.</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:18:49.920 --> 00:18:50.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( computer beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:18:51.547 --> 00:18:53.006 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Navigation just went offline.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:18:53.090 --> 00:18:55.008 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's the particle flux in the nebula.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:18:55.092 --> 00:18:57.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-It's overloading the sensors.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I've lost them.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:18:57.845 --> 00:19:00.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can we compensate for the flux?</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:19:00.806 --> 00:19:02.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It'll take a few hours.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:19:02.766 --> 00:19:04.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have the bridge.</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:19:08.605 --> 00:19:10.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs )</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:19:11.441 --> 00:19:13.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain, you need to rest.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:19:13.610 --> 00:19:15.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thanks, but I'll be fine.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:19:15.237 --> 00:19:17.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The atmosphere is thinner</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>than you're used to.</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:19:17.948 --> 00:19:20.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't stop soon, you'll collapse.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:19:20.492 --> 00:19:24.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you need a break, T'Pol,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you should say so.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:19:24.246 --> 00:19:25.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to scout ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:19:34.464 --> 00:19:36.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you had any more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>conversations with Surak?</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:19:37.009 --> 00:19:38.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not in a couple of hours.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:19:38.760 --> 00:19:40.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:19:40.512 --> 00:19:41.638 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:19:41.722 --> 00:19:43.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Something's amusing?</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:19:43.807 --> 00:19:47.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of all the people who could have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>carried this Katra.</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:19:47.352 --> 00:19:49.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I doubt you were Syrran's first choice.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:19:49.605 --> 00:19:55.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ever since the meld,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I've felt more... centered.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:19:56.486 --> 00:19:58.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's hard to explain.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:19:59.573 --> 00:20:01.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My whole life,</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:20:01.283 --> 00:20:04.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've never really understood Vulcans...</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:20:05.537 --> 00:20:08.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why they work so hard</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to suppress their emotions.</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:20:10.292 --> 00:20:12.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now it all seems to make sense.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:20:13.045 --> 00:20:15.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Next thing you know,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll be taking up meditation.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:20:16.089 --> 00:20:18.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You might find it beneficial.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:20:18.300 --> 00:20:19.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckles )</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:20:20.552 --> 00:20:24.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After we get back,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>maybe you'll want to take a closer look</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:20:24.264 --> 00:20:25.724 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>at the Syrrannites' philosophy.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:20:26.892 --> 00:20:27.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why?</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:20:28.018 --> 00:20:30.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( sighs ) It was important to your mother.</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:20:30.854 --> 00:20:32.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There might be something to it.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:20:33.732 --> 00:20:38.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are many groups who claim to follow</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the true path of Surak.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:20:38.737 --> 00:20:41.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I find no evidence</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that this one's any different.</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:20:41.740 --> 00:20:44.576 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would've thought you'd be more</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sympathetic to their cause.</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:20:45.369 --> 00:20:48.664 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You never seemed too happy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the status quo around here.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:20:48.747 --> 00:20:50.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I may have had disagreements</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the High Command,</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:20:51.041 --> 00:20:53.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but that doesn't mean</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to join a radical faction.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:20:55.128 --> 00:20:57.965 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You signed up with Starfleet.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:20:58.507 --> 00:21:01.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>A lot of Vulcans I've met</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>consider us a radical faction.</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:21:03.387 --> 00:21:05.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>As a scientist,</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:21:05.931 --> 00:21:07.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just thought you might want</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to keep an open mind about it.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:21:07.766 --> 00:21:09.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This has nothing to do with science!</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:21:09.601 --> 00:21:11.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Am I interrupting?</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:21:15.232 --> 00:21:16.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:21:29.746 --> 00:21:32.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Let me out of here!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I can't.</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:21:32.165 --> 00:21:33.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry. Not yet.</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:21:34.042 --> 00:21:36.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll tear the antennae from your skull!</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:21:36.086 --> 00:21:39.006 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If this interrogation continues,</c.bg_transparent>

369
00:21:39.089 --> 00:21:42.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>your suppression system</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>could be permanently damaged.</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:21:42.467 --> 00:21:43.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell me what I want to know!</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:21:43.969 --> 00:21:46.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aren't you enjoying this, Commander?</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:21:46.930 --> 00:21:50.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Have you imagined having me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in this chair many times?</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:21:51.018 --> 00:21:53.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not far from the truth.</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:21:53.854 --> 00:21:58.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But after our rather lengthy peace talks,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I came to trust you.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:21:58.817 --> 00:22:00.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then trust me now!</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:22:01.111 --> 00:22:03.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You would never betray your people!</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:22:03.780 --> 00:22:05.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm trying to save them!</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:22:05.782 --> 00:22:07.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:22:09.911 --> 00:22:12.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where is your fleet?</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:22:12.205 --> 00:22:14.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( panting )</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:22:16.251 --> 00:22:18.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you know the story of Nirak?</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:22:20.047 --> 00:22:21.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What?</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:22:21.256 --> 00:22:24.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was a soldier</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>who lived a long time ago.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:22:24.926 --> 00:22:29.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was standing watch over</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the gates of the city of Gol,</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:22:29.598 --> 00:22:33.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and he saw a cloud on the horizon</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>moving toward him.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:22:33.977 --> 00:22:37.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He thought it was a sandstorm,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>so he told no one.</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:22:37.731 --> 00:22:40.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It was an army.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:22:40.192 --> 00:22:44.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They destroyed the city,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but they let Nirak live.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:22:44.946 --> 00:22:50.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>His name now means "Fool" in our language,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>just as yours will in Andorian!</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:22:54.581 --> 00:22:56.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( electronic whining )</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:22:56.374 --> 00:22:58.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( screaming )</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:23:05.425 --> 00:23:07.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Give the Kir'Shara to us.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:23:07.761 --> 00:23:09.304 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You won't be injured.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:23:12.182 --> 00:23:14.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This isn't your world, human.</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:23:14.935 --> 00:23:16.937 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:24:14.119 --> 00:24:15.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Archer!</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:24:15.745 --> 00:24:18.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Surrender and you won't be harmed.</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:24:19.166 --> 00:24:20.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not leaving her.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:24:52.616 --> 00:24:53.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( coughing )</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:24:53.825 --> 00:24:55.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh.</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:24:55.744 --> 00:24:57.579 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( panting )</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:25:00.332 --> 00:25:02.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What the hell were you doing?</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:25:02.167 --> 00:25:04.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Protecting the Kir'Shara.</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:25:15.430 --> 00:25:17.057 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:25:17.140 --> 00:25:19.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where are they taking the Kir'Shara?</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:25:24.189 --> 00:25:27.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Mount Seleya.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Why?</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:25:27.192 --> 00:25:31.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because the artifact contains</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Surak's original writings.</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:25:31.488 --> 00:25:34.616 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Only the priests on Seleya</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can translate them.</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:25:35.533 --> 00:25:37.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you are deceiving me...</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:25:37.869 --> 00:25:40.205 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I am a Syrrannite. We don't lie.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:25:54.552 --> 00:25:55.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moans )</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:25:55.929 --> 00:25:58.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( panting ) I need to rest.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:25:58.640 --> 00:26:00.767 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you're attempting to delay us,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it won't work.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:26:00.850 --> 00:26:02.310 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll find your friends.</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:26:11.111 --> 00:26:13.947 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've changed.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:26:14.030 --> 00:26:17.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I served under you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>during the Tomed mission.</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:26:17.325 --> 00:26:18.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't remember me.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:26:18.702 --> 00:26:20.370 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's a very long time ago.</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:26:21.329 --> 00:26:23.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You were a fine officer then.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:26:24.040 --> 00:26:27.085 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why did you betray us?</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:26:27.669 --> 00:26:29.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They must have offered you something.</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:26:30.463 --> 00:26:32.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Or perhaps you enjoy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hiding bombs in embassies.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:26:32.924 --> 00:26:34.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We weren't responsible.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:26:34.634 --> 00:26:36.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Two of my men were killed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the embassy explosion.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:26:37.053 --> 00:26:38.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You have been misled.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:26:39.472 --> 00:26:40.932 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Syrrannites are peaceful.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:26:41.599 --> 00:26:44.686 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have spared your life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>because you were once my superior.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:26:44.769 --> 00:26:47.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your companions won't be so fortunate.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:26:49.065 --> 00:26:52.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-FEMALE: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Bridge to Commander Shran.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What is it?</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:26:52.444 --> 00:26:54.696 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>The general is asking for</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>an update on the interrogation.</i></c.bg_transparent>

431
00:26:54.779 --> 00:26:56.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell him I'll contact him when I'm ready.</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:26:56.698 --> 00:26:58.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Acknowledged.</i></c.bg_transparent>

433
00:26:58.158 --> 00:27:00.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:27:01.953 --> 00:27:04.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You find this amusing?</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:27:05.081 --> 00:27:09.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ordinarily I wouldn't,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but because of this device...</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:27:09.878 --> 00:27:14.132 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are three higher settings</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on that panel.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:27:14.716 --> 00:27:17.052 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I use them...</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:27:18.178 --> 00:27:20.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're afraid to injure me.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:27:21.473 --> 00:27:25.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I were you, I'd leave that detail out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in your report to the general.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:27:26.227 --> 00:27:28.688 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where is your fleet?</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:27:29.064 --> 00:27:31.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was a fool to think you'd listen.</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:27:31.983 --> 00:27:33.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perhaps the High Command was right.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:27:34.402 --> 00:27:37.072 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We'll be better off when Andoria falls.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:27:37.155 --> 00:27:38.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( explosion )</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:27:38.948 --> 00:27:40.158 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Report!</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:27:40.241 --> 00:27:42.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>FEMALE: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>It's the Starfleet ship.</i></c.bg_transparent>

447
00:27:42.452 --> 00:27:43.787 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Direct hit to their shield generator.</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:27:43.870 --> 00:27:45.914 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>See if you can get a lock on Soval.</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:27:47.415 --> 00:27:49.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>FEMALE: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Should we return fire?</i></c.bg_transparent>

450
00:27:49.084 --> 00:27:52.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you going to make enemies</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the humans as well?</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:27:58.343 --> 00:28:01.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lieutenant,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>order our ships out of the nebula.</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:28:01.513 --> 00:28:03.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-FEMALE: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Commander?</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-And tell </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise</i></c.bg_transparent>

453
00:28:03.348 --> 00:28:05.809 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>we'll be returning the ambassador shortly.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:28:05.892 --> 00:28:07.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Understood.</i></c.bg_transparent>

455
00:28:07.560 --> 00:28:09.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get that thing off of him.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:28:17.695 --> 00:28:21.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're heading east,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>away from the capital.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:28:23.535 --> 00:28:25.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's with them.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:28:28.790 --> 00:28:30.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Where are you going?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-To find my science officer.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:28:30.959 --> 00:28:33.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And I don't want to hear any lectures</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about the needs of the many.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:28:33.628 --> 00:28:35.755 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I get enough of that crap from...</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:28:36.631 --> 00:28:38.383 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>From T'Pol.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:28:38.466 --> 00:28:40.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no logic to your plan.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:28:40.719 --> 00:28:42.095 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have no weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:28:42.178 --> 00:28:44.806 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If they take the Kir'Shara from you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they'll destroy it.</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:28:44.889 --> 00:28:46.307 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm gonna find her.</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:29:04.117 --> 00:29:05.243 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How is he?</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:29:05.326 --> 00:29:07.454 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've got a lot of nerve</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>pretending you give a damn.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:29:07.537 --> 00:29:09.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did what was necessary.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:29:10.999 --> 00:29:12.667 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Soval would understand.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:29:13.334 --> 00:29:15.587 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He should be fine in another day or so.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:29:15.670 --> 00:29:17.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He risked his life coming here.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:29:17.672 --> 00:29:19.799 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you paid him back</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by scrambling his neurons.</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:29:19.883 --> 00:29:22.552 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He is not the only one taking a risk.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:29:22.635 --> 00:29:25.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I just spoke with the Imperial Guard.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:29:25.472 --> 00:29:28.099 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're redeploying our forces.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:29:29.058 --> 00:29:30.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now you believe him.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:29:30.935 --> 00:29:32.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What changed your mind?</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:29:34.105 --> 00:29:36.149 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A lesser man would have told me</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:29:36.232 --> 00:29:38.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>what I wanted to hear,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even if it wasn't true.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:29:39.402 --> 00:29:45.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's been too much suspicion,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>too many lies, on both sides.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:29:48.369 --> 00:29:52.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our fleet will intercept the Vulcans</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at these coordinates.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:29:52.165 --> 00:29:58.421 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>My superiors believe it may be...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>helpful if </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enterprise </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>were to join us.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:30:04.135 --> 00:30:06.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( screeching )</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:30:06.137 --> 00:30:07.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sehlat.</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:30:11.267 --> 00:30:14.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( imitating screeching )</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:30:18.066 --> 00:30:19.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:30:36.125 --> 00:30:38.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My First Officer... Where is she?</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:30:43.174 --> 00:30:44.551 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What have you done with her?</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:30:45.593 --> 00:30:49.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's been taken to the High Command.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:30:59.232 --> 00:31:01.568 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your technique has improved.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:31:08.575 --> 00:31:12.036 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Welcome home, Subcommander.</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:31:13.705 --> 00:31:15.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I no longer hold that rank.</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:31:15.582 --> 00:31:17.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, you may have joined Starfleet,</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:31:17.292 --> 00:31:21.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but you're still Vulcan</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and subject to our laws.</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:31:22.338 --> 00:31:26.050 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are few crimes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>still punishable by execution,</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:31:26.134 --> 00:31:28.469 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but treason is one of them.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:31:28.553 --> 00:31:30.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( computer beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:31:30.805 --> 00:31:32.140 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What is it?</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:31:32.223 --> 00:31:36.603 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Seven alien ships have taken position</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>outside the Andorian system.</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:31:36.686 --> 00:31:39.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They're directly in the path of our fleet.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:31:46.154 --> 00:31:49.157 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you sure this is wise?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>If the Vulcans find us here,</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:31:49.240 --> 00:31:50.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>they might think we're siding</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with the Andorians.</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:31:50.909 --> 00:31:53.077 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no guarantee</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they won't fire on us.</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:31:53.161 --> 00:31:56.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sir, I'm reading a massive</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>subspace distortion.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:31:56.539 --> 00:31:57.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hoshi?</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:31:57.832 --> 00:31:59.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's the Vulcans.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They'll be here in two hours.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:31:59.959 --> 00:32:01.127 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( computer beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:32:01.210 --> 00:32:02.295 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's hailing us again.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:32:02.378 --> 00:32:03.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On screen.</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:32:05.089 --> 00:32:08.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Our sensors show</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>12 Vulcan cruisers approaching.</i></c.bg_transparent>

511
00:32:08.718 --> 00:32:10.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>When will the rest of your fleet get here?</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:32:10.511 --> 00:32:13.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>They won't arrive in time.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>We're on our own.</i></c.bg_transparent>

513
00:32:20.855 --> 00:32:24.943 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: I'm still not clear</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how the Kir'Shara is gonna stop a war.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:32:25.026 --> 00:32:27.737 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>V'Las can't govern without</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>approval from the Council.</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:32:28.321 --> 00:32:29.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The existence of the Kir'Shara</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:32:30.073 --> 00:32:33.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>will persuade them</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to reconsider their support.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:32:37.497 --> 00:32:41.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't suppose they'll let us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>just walk into the High Command.</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:32:41.626 --> 00:32:44.671 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We can transport in,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but we'll need access codes.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:32:46.923 --> 00:32:48.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know someone who might have them.</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:33:00.103 --> 00:33:01.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Vulcans are powering weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:33:01.521 --> 00:33:03.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Andorians are doing the same.</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:33:03.106 --> 00:33:05.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Travis, put us between both fleets.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:33:05.441 --> 00:33:07.485 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If the Vulcans want to start a war,</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:33:07.568 --> 00:33:10.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>they're gonna</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have to get through us first.</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:33:10.530 --> 00:33:13.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( computer beeps )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's Shran.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:33:14.993 --> 00:33:16.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SHRAN: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Commander,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>what do you think you're doing?</i></c.bg_transparent>

527
00:33:16.786 --> 00:33:19.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In case you hadn't noticed,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they outnumber us two to one!</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:33:19.372 --> 00:33:22.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>-Get back in formation.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm trying to buy us some time!</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:33:28.006 --> 00:33:30.883 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Andorians have more ships on the way.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:33:30.967 --> 00:33:32.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They won't arrive for several hours.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:33:32.885 --> 00:33:36.097 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You told us this strike</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>would be a surprise,</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:33:36.180 --> 00:33:39.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>that there would be minimal</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>casualties on both sides.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:33:39.600 --> 00:33:43.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Andorians are armed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>with standard particle cannons.</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:33:43.354 --> 00:33:47.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There is no evidence of Xindi technology.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:33:47.692 --> 00:33:51.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Administrator,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we have to call off this attack.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:33:53.197 --> 00:33:55.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Our forces are committed.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:33:55.324 --> 00:33:57.452 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-We can't turn back.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-( computer beeps )</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:33:57.535 --> 00:33:59.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALE: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>We're being hailed</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>by the Starfleet ship.</i></c.bg_transparent>

539
00:34:01.456 --> 00:34:04.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>This is Commander Tucker.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Sorry to spoil your surprise,</i></c.bg_transparent>

540
00:34:04.584 --> 00:34:06.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>but the Andorians know</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>what you're planning.</i></c.bg_transparent>

541
00:34:06.919 --> 00:34:09.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suggest you turn your ships around now.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:34:09.422 --> 00:34:13.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This doesn't concern Starfleet.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Leave the area immediately.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:34:13.468 --> 00:34:14.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't do that.</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:34:15.053 --> 00:34:16.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Andorians helped us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when Earth was under attack.</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:34:17.013 --> 00:34:18.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're just here to return the favor.</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:34:19.015 --> 00:34:21.934 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you side with the Andorians,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you'll be fired upon.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:34:22.018 --> 00:34:24.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>I've already sent word</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>to Admiral Gardner.</i></c.bg_transparent>

548
00:34:24.437 --> 00:34:28.649 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>If </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>Enterprise </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>is destroyed,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Starfleet's gonna know who is responsible.</i></c.bg_transparent>

549
00:34:30.234 --> 00:34:34.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Order our ships to engage the enemy fleet.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:34:34.363 --> 00:34:37.617 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Administrator, I can't allow this.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:34:38.326 --> 00:34:40.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sublieutenant.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:34:40.578 --> 00:34:43.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you attempt to interfere again...</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:34:44.916 --> 00:34:46.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have you arrested.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:34:50.254 --> 00:34:51.589 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( computer beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:34:51.672 --> 00:34:53.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Vulcans... They're locking weapons.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:34:53.883 --> 00:34:55.093 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On us?</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:34:55.176 --> 00:34:58.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-No. Just the Andorians.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Stand by phase cannons.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:34:58.471 --> 00:35:00.098 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't fire until I give the order.</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:35:13.402 --> 00:35:14.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're in the crossfire!</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:35:15.029 --> 00:35:17.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hard about.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Get us out of their weapons range.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:35:17.240 --> 00:35:20.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>One of the Andorian ships is in trouble.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Their reactor's been hit.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:35:20.284 --> 00:35:21.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A Vulcan cruiser's heading towards them.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:35:21.869 --> 00:35:23.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>See if you can get their attention.</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:35:25.414 --> 00:35:28.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALE: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>The Earth vessel's opened fire</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>on one of our ships.</i></c.bg_transparent>

565
00:35:28.126 --> 00:35:29.836 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Destroy them.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:35:29.919 --> 00:35:31.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The cruiser's breaking off its attack.</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:35:31.963 --> 00:35:33.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-We're being targeted.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-( explosion )</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:35:33.589 --> 00:35:36.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Evasive starboard. Full impulse.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:35:36.467 --> 00:35:37.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Malcolm!</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:35:37.510 --> 00:35:39.679 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're not making a dent in their shields.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:35:48.604 --> 00:35:50.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( computer beeps )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Shran's hailing.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:35:54.735 --> 00:35:57.363 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Tell Archer that's two he owes me!</i></c.bg_transparent>

573
00:36:13.504 --> 00:36:14.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Contact security!</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:36:14.922 --> 00:36:18.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stay where you are.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We need to have a talk.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:36:18.676 --> 00:36:22.013 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Administrator,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it is agreeable to see you again.</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:36:22.680 --> 00:36:26.726 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This woman is an anarchist, Captain.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:36:27.727 --> 00:36:30.438 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Whatever she's told you isn't the truth.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:36:30.521 --> 00:36:33.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'Pau didn't bomb our embassy.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:36:34.984 --> 00:36:36.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You did.</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:36:37.111 --> 00:36:39.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The evidence is conclusive.</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:36:39.488 --> 00:36:41.824 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Evidence your people gave us.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:36:41.908 --> 00:36:46.245 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The bombing was an excuse</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to round up the Syrrannites,</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:36:46.329 --> 00:36:49.540 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to make certain they'd never find this.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:36:57.089 --> 00:36:58.633 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that...</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:36:59.300 --> 00:37:01.093 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Kir'Shara is a myth!</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:37:27.787 --> 00:37:29.747 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Hull plating's gone!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Torpedoes!</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:37:29.830 --> 00:37:31.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The launchers aren't responding.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:37:31.457 --> 00:37:33.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where the hell is Shran?</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:37:33.084 --> 00:37:34.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Vulcans are keeping him busy.</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:37:35.920 --> 00:37:38.172 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Looks like we really are on our own.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:37:38.673 --> 00:37:42.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Holographic trickery. This proves nothing.</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:37:42.260 --> 00:37:45.012 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The artifact must be examined in detail.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:37:45.638 --> 00:37:46.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:37:46.806 --> 00:37:49.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quantum dating will confirm that</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it's from the time of Surak.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:37:49.934 --> 00:37:51.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't trust her!</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:37:51.560 --> 00:37:54.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She'd do anything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to spread her deviant beliefs.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:37:54.438 --> 00:37:56.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've spent years trying to subvert me.</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:37:56.482 --> 00:37:58.734 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Kir'Shara will show us our true path.</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:37:58.818 --> 00:38:01.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They'd kill us all if they had the chance!</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:38:01.988 --> 00:38:03.990 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It must be destroyed!</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:38:09.537 --> 00:38:11.539 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is Minister Kuvak.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:38:11.622 --> 00:38:14.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get me the Fleet Commander immediately.</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:38:14.166 --> 00:38:17.003 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( alarm blares )</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:38:17.086 --> 00:38:19.130 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've lost helm control.</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:38:19.213 --> 00:38:22.508 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hull breach on "G" deck.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We're venting atmosphere.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:38:30.474 --> 00:38:33.311 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Vulcan ships... They're withdrawing.</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:38:33.394 --> 00:38:35.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( computer beeps )</c.bg_transparent>

608
00:38:35.354 --> 00:38:38.024 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're being hailed. It's the High Command.</c.bg_transparent>

609
00:38:40.609 --> 00:38:43.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Trip, is everything all right?</i></c.bg_transparent>

610
00:38:43.946 --> 00:38:46.032 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>More or less.</c.bg_transparent>

611
00:38:46.115 --> 00:38:48.117 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's going on, Captain?</c.bg_transparent>

612
00:38:48.200 --> 00:38:50.244 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>There have been a few changes here.</i></c.bg_transparent>

613
00:38:50.328 --> 00:38:52.371 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Get back to Vulcan as soon as you can.</i></c.bg_transparent>

614
00:38:54.707 --> 00:38:56.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>ARCHER: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Captain's starlog, supplemental.</i></c.bg_transparent>

615
00:38:57.043 --> 00:39:00.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Administrator V'Las has been</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>relieved of his position.</i></c.bg_transparent>

616
00:39:00.379 --> 00:39:03.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>His role in the embassy bombing</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>is being investigated.</i></c.bg_transparent>

617
00:39:03.549 --> 00:39:06.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>For the moment,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>the conflict between Vulcan and Andoria</i></c.bg_transparent>

618
00:39:07.053 --> 00:39:08.846 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>appears to have been averted.</i></c.bg_transparent>

619
00:39:09.930 --> 00:39:11.265 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>T'POL: </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Enter.</i></c.bg_transparent>

620
00:39:14.060 --> 00:39:17.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Captain Archer asked me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to express his gratitude.</c.bg_transparent>

621
00:39:17.480 --> 00:39:20.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He wouldn't have succeeded</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>without your transporter codes.</c.bg_transparent>

622
00:39:20.566 --> 00:39:23.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Captain told me you were in danger.</c.bg_transparent>

623
00:39:23.694 --> 00:39:26.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wouldn't have been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a very good husband if I didn't help.</c.bg_transparent>

624
00:39:26.906 --> 00:39:29.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not certain</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when I'll be able to return.</c.bg_transparent>

625
00:39:30.326 --> 00:39:33.913 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm aware that I promised your family</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that we would eventually live together.</c.bg_transparent>

626
00:39:33.996 --> 00:39:35.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's not why I've come.</c.bg_transparent>

627
00:39:35.831 --> 00:39:38.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm releasing you from our marriage.</c.bg_transparent>

628
00:39:38.959 --> 00:39:42.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know you only bonded with me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to help your mother.</c.bg_transparent>

629
00:39:43.214 --> 00:39:44.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's gone now.</c.bg_transparent>

630
00:39:45.549 --> 00:39:47.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's no reason for us to continue.</c.bg_transparent>

631
00:39:48.844 --> 00:39:50.471 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You don't have to do this.</c.bg_transparent>

632
00:39:50.554 --> 00:39:51.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know.</c.bg_transparent>

633
00:39:56.394 --> 00:39:57.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Koss.</c.bg_transparent>

634
00:40:00.856 --> 00:40:01.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Goodbye, T'Pol.</c.bg_transparent>

635
00:40:22.086 --> 00:40:24.213 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Katra is with me now.</c.bg_transparent>

636
00:40:26.382 --> 00:40:27.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How do you feel, Captain?</c.bg_transparent>

637
00:40:32.138 --> 00:40:33.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Like a giant weight's been lifted.</c.bg_transparent>

638
00:40:34.265 --> 00:40:37.017 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Word has already spread of the discovery.</c.bg_transparent>

639
00:40:37.101 --> 00:40:40.396 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It may take years</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to translate all of the writings.</c.bg_transparent>

640
00:40:40.479 --> 00:40:43.315 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The people of Vulcan are in your debt.</c.bg_transparent>

641
00:40:44.775 --> 00:40:47.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Peace and long life.</c.bg_transparent>

642
00:40:53.117 --> 00:40:55.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You may be witnessing</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the start of a new era,</c.bg_transparent>

643
00:40:55.661 --> 00:40:58.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not only for Vulcan,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but for Earth as well.</c.bg_transparent>

644
00:40:58.789 --> 00:41:00.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Minister intends to pursue</c.bg_transparent>

645
00:41:00.666 --> 00:41:03.002 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>a less aggressive policy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>toward your people.</c.bg_transparent>

646
00:41:03.085 --> 00:41:05.588 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The High Command will be dissolved.</c.bg_transparent>

647
00:41:05.671 --> 00:41:07.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll no longer have us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>looking over your shoulder.</c.bg_transparent>

648
00:41:07.882 --> 00:41:10.718 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's time for Earth to stand on its own.</c.bg_transparent>

649
00:41:11.302 --> 00:41:12.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We're ready.</c.bg_transparent>

650
00:41:19.727 --> 00:41:21.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You've failed!</c.bg_transparent>

651
00:41:21.479 --> 00:41:23.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Decades of work have been lost.</c.bg_transparent>

652
00:41:23.647 --> 00:41:25.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>MALE: Am I to be blamed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for your incompetence?</c.bg_transparent>

653
00:41:26.025 --> 00:41:27.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Archer should have been killed!</c.bg_transparent>

654
00:41:27.485 --> 00:41:29.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You brought the humans into this.</c.bg_transparent>

655
00:41:29.987 --> 00:41:31.155 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I must leave Vulcan.</c.bg_transparent>

656
00:41:31.238 --> 00:41:33.115 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My position here has been compromised.</c.bg_transparent>

657
00:41:33.199 --> 00:41:34.366 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What about me?</c.bg_transparent>

658
00:41:34.450 --> 00:41:35.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not now.</c.bg_transparent>

659
00:41:36.035 --> 00:41:38.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your disappearance would cause suspicion.</c.bg_transparent>

660
00:41:39.163 --> 00:41:41.373 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is simply a minor delay.</c.bg_transparent>

661
00:41:41.457 --> 00:41:44.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The reunification of our people</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is only a matter of time.</c.bg_transparent>

